4.5.2.2. CMake
box2d

set(BOX2D_BUILD_UNIT_TESTS OFF CACHE BOOL "" FORCE)

box2d
URL https://github.com/erincatto/box2d/archive/refs/tags/v2.4.1.tar.
gz
)
FetchContent_MakeAvailable(box2d)
target_link_libraries(your_target_name box2d)
